Hi, everyone.

I am having a bit of trouble digging up references to endofunctors with the
following property:

Hom(F(A (x) B),C) = Hom(A, F(A) => C)

where * => * is the internal hom.

I am interested in work where this property is induced by additional
structure, but even more interested in ones where this is not induced and
is an axiom.

The functor I am working with is a comonad, but I am interested in more
than just comonads.

Thanks,
Harley


